  "body": "Hi all,\r\n\r\nWe have a bug which can be reproduced as follows: setup a beacon node that is waiting for the ChainStart log from the deposit contract and connect a validator client to it. Then, shut down the beacon node process. The validator client will all of a sudden believe ChainStart was reached at time.Unix(0, 0) and begin performing its responsibility eternally. This is not the desired behavior.",
